Query the UniProt REST API

Source: R/analysis_information.R
queryUniprot.Rd

Query the UniProt REST API

Usage

queryUniprot(molecule, format = "xml")

Arguments

molecule

Character: protein or transcript to query

format

Character: format of the response

Value

Parsed response

Examples

protein <- "P51587"
format <- "xml"
psichomics:::queryUniprot(protein, format)
